<p>Your two favorite Mac geeks are back for a second-installment with this week&rsquo;s Premium episode. Discussing Dropbox security, rearranging Login Items, how to manage your Mac&rsquo;s menubar, home networking and more, John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton keep you informed and entertained. Subscribe today, support the guys, and learn in the process!</p>
